<i>is truly a
sight of beauty!</i>

00:18:08.475 --> 00:18:09.411
[water bubbling]

00:18:09.444 --> 00:18:10.614
- Huh?

00:18:10.648 --> 00:18:11.850
[roaring]

00:18:11.883 --> 00:18:13.185
- Whoa!

00:18:13.218 --> 00:18:15.891
[all groaning]

00:18:15.924 --> 00:18:17.427
