00:18:17.460 --> 00:18:22.037
AKIRA: There's so many of them!

00:18:22.070 --> 00:18:23.807
[all breathing heavily]

00:18:23.840 --> 00:18:25.142
SHIZUKA: Oh, well!

00:18:25.176 --> 00:18:27.748
I guess we're not kicking back
in a hot spring!

00:18:27.782 --> 00:18:29.350
BEATRIX: So disappointing!

00:18:29.384 --> 00:18:32.490
I wanted to visit all
the famous locations!

00:18:32.525 --> 00:18:35.831
KENCHO: Aww, just when Bea
was about to bathe with us, too!

00:18:35.864 --> 00:18:37.033
- [whimpering]

00:18:37.066 --> 00:18:38.837
[screaming]

00:18:38.870 --> 00:18:41.074
