00:19:26.733 --> 00:19:27.902
[gasps]

00:19:27.935 --> 00:19:30.139
No way.

00:19:30.173 --> 00:19:32.577
A hot spring in the middle
of the mountains!

00:19:33.580 --> 00:19:37.119
Ah!

00:19:37.153 --> 00:19:40.092
This one feels even better
than the last one!

00:19:40.125 --> 00:19:42.565
I bet heaven's got nothin'
on this.

00:19:42.598 --> 00:19:44.334
No way.

00:19:44.367 --> 00:19:46.572
[SHIZUKA screams]
[AKIRA grunts]

00:19:47.541 --> 00:19:48.577
Huh?

00:19:48.610 --> 00:19:51.181
[SHIZUKA gasping]
AKIRA: Sh--Sh--Shizuka?

00:19:51.214 --> 00:19:52.851
- [whimpering]

00:19:52.884 --> 00:19:54.487
[both shouting]

00:19:54.522 --> 00:19:56.659
AKIRA: Sorry! I seriously
didn't know you were in here.

00:19:56.692 --> 00:19:58.596
It really was an accident!
I promise!

00:19:58.629 --> 00:20:02.003
- I don't care what it
was! Hurry up and get out!

00:20:02.036 --> 00:20:03.973
- Wait, what?
Hey, that's not fair!

00:20:04.006 --> 00:20:05.910
I just got here!
- Wha--what?

00:20:05.944 --> 00:20:09.384
- All I wanted to do here
was kick back in a hot spring,

00:20:09.417 --> 00:20:12.558
and if I have to leave
this place without doing that,

00:20:12.591 --> 00:20:14.995
