As long as you stay on
the other side of that boulder.

00:20:28.022 --> 00:20:29.390
Okay?
- Okay!

00:20:29.424 --> 00:20:31.495
- But if you turn around,
you're dead!

00:20:31.529 --> 00:20:32.597
- Okay!

00:20:32.631 --> 00:20:33.633
- [grunts]

00:20:36.004 --> 00:20:37.808
- [shuddering]

00:20:43.452 --> 00:20:44.988
SHIZUKA: About earlier.

00:20:45.022 --> 00:20:46.191
I'm sorry.

00:20:46.224 --> 00:20:47.695
- Huh?

00:20:47.728 --> 00:20:51.000
SHIZUKA: Back when I shot down
your ideas about love.

00:20:52.470 --> 00:20:54.609
My father didn't--well,

00:20:54.642 --> 00:20:57.647
he never approved
of how I lived my life.

00:20:57.681 --> 00:21:00.019
